text: Omosarotes nigripennis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Zajciw in 1970. It is known from Brazil.BioLib.cz - Omosarotes nigripennis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Cyrtinini Category:Beetles described in 1970
